{"word":"G520 - ἀπάγω - apágō - ap-ag'-o - Bring","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπάγω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apágō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-ag'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Bring</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - போ, கொண்டுபோ, செலுத்து"},{"paragraph":"to lead away"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G71 - ἄγω - ágō - ag'-o/71\">G71</a>; to <i>take off</i> (in various senses): - bring, carry away, lead (away), put to death, take away.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}